# Multi-Vendor E-Commerce Store

Final Year Project

This project is a Multi-Vendor E-Commerce platform developed using PHP and MySQL.

## Features
- Vendor registration and login
- Vendor dashboard for product management
- Product listing for customers
- Shopping cart
- Checkout system
- Order history

## Technologies
- PHP
- MySQL
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

